{"word":"John","slug":"john","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>John</b> 1. The Baptist:<br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=40&verse=3'>Isa 40:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=4&verse=6'>Mal 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=17'>Luk 1:17</a> <br/> - Miraculous birth of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=20'>Luk 1:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=65'>Luk 1:65</a> <br/> - Dwells in the desert<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=1'>Mat 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=4'>Mar 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=80'>Luk 1:80</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=3'>Luk 3:3</a> <br/> - Mission of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=11'>Mat 17:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=8'>Mar 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=17'>Luk 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=79'>Luk 1:79</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=6'>Luk 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=8'>Joh 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=15'>Joh 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=28'>Joh 1:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=34'>Joh 1:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=35'>Joh 5:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=25'>Act 13:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=4'>Act 19:4</a> <br/> - Ministry of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=3'>Mat 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=4'>Mar 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=3'>Luk 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=8'>Joh 1:8</a> <br/> - His influence upon the public mind<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=6'>Mat 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=5'>Mat 14:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=32'>Mat 21:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=5'>Mar 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=11&verse=32'>Mar 11:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=7'>Luk 3:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=15'>Luk 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=20&verse=6'>Luk 20:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=40'>Joh 1:40</a> <br/> - Testifies to the messiahship of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=12'>Mat 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=8'>Mar 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=17'>Luk 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=15'>Joh 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=36'>Joh 1:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=36'>Joh 3:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=33'>Joh 5:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=41'>Joh 10:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=25'>Act 13:25</a> <br/> - Teaches his disciples:<br/> b to pray<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=1'>Luk 11:1</a><br/> b to fast<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=33'>Luk 5:33</a><br/> - The baptism which he taught<br/> <a href='S:Baptism'>Baptism</a> <br/> - Baptizes Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=16'>Mat 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=11'>Mar 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=22'>Luk 3:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=32'>Joh 1:32</a> <br/> - The testimony of Jesus concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=35'>Joh 5:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=13'>Mat 17:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=32'>Mat 21:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=13'>Mar 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=19'>Mat 11:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=33'>Luk 7:33</a> <br/> - His ministry not attested by miracles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=41'>Joh 10:41</a> <br/> - Reproves Herod on account of his incest; Herod imprisons him; beheads him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=12'>Mat 4:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=12'>Mat 14:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=29'>Mar 6:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=13'>Mar 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=20'>Luk 3:20</a> <br/> - Sends two disciples to Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=6'>Mat 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=23'>Luk 7:23</a> <br/> - Herod falsely supposes Jesus to be<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=2'>Mat 14:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=14'>Mat 16:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=14'>Mar 6:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=16'>Mar 6:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=19'>Luk 9:19</a> <br/> - Character of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=20'>Mar 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=35'>Joh 5:35</a> <br/> - Jesus discourses upon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=19'>Mat 11:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=33'>Luk 7:33</a> <br/> - Affected probably by the doctrines of the stoics<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=18'>Mat 11:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=6'>Mar 1:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=80'>Luk 1:80</a> <br/> - A Nazarite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=18'>Mat 11:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=15'>Luk 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=33'>Luk 7:33</a> <br/> 2. The Apostle:<br/> - Intimately associated with Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=26'>Joh 13:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=20'>Joh 21:20</a> <br/> - Is present when Jesus performs the following miracles:<br/> b Healing of Peter's mother-in-law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=15'>Mat 8:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=31'>Mar 1:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=39'>Luk 4:39</a><br/> b Raising of the daughter of Jairus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=37'>Mar 5:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=51'>Luk 8:51</a><br/> b the two draughts of fishes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=10'>Luk 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=7'>Joh 21:7</a><br/> b Transfiguration<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=1'>Mat 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=2'>Mar 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=28'>Luk 9:28</a><br/> - Is present with Jesus in the garden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=37'>Mat 26:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=33'>Mar 14:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=39'>Luk 22:39</a> <br/> - Intolerance of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=38'>Mar 9:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=50'>Luk 9:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=56'>Luk 9:56</a> <br/> - Civil ambitions of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=20&verse=24'>Mat 20:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=41'>Mar 10:41</a> <br/> - Prepares the Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=19'>Mat 26:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=16'>Mar 14:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=13'>Luk 22:13</a> <br/> - Present:<br/> b at the trial of Jesus before the high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=16'>Joh 18:16</a><br/> b at the crucifixion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=27'>Joh 19:27</a><br/> b at the sepulcher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=8'>Joh 20:8</a><br/> b When Jesus manifested Himself at the Sea of Galilee<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21'>Joh 21</a><br/> b With Peter in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=3&verse=11'>Act 3:11</a><br/> - Dwells in Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a> <br/> - Is entrusted with the care of Mary, mother of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=26'>Joh 19:26</a> <br/> - Imprisoned by the rulers of the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=19'>Act 4:19</a> <br/> - Sent by the church with the commission to Samaria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=17'>Act 8:17</a> <br/> - A pillar of the church<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=9'>Gal 2:9</a> <br/> - Writes to the churches<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=1'>1Jn 1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=63&chapter=1&verse=13'>2Jn 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=64&chapter=1&verse=14'>3Jn 1:14</a> <br/> - Writes his apocalyptic vision from Patmos<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=9'>Rev 1:9</a> <br/> - Prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=10&verse=11'>Rev 10:11</a> <br/> 3. A kinsman of Annas the high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=6'>Act 4:6</a><br/> 4. Whose surname was Mark<br/> <a href='S:Mark'>Mark</a>"}]}